strings:
<voice_0x01001424><se_low>Gemon: Impossible!
N-No human could be so strong...
<voice_0x01001425><se_low>Gemon: Of course! Empyrea! She brought you here from the World of Light to defeat me!

<voice_0x01001426><se_low>Gemon: What a fool to think she could get the better
of me!
<voice_0x01001427><se_low>Gemon: If I die, I'm taking her egg with me!

<voice_0x01001428><se_low>Gemon: She'll regret the day she tried to trick Gemon!
Gwa ha ha ha hah!

<voice_0x0100142A><center>W-What!? What happened!?
<center>My egg.... My baby...in pieces...
<voice_0x0100142B><se_high>Jessica: Empyrea, I... I'm so sorry...

<voice_0x0100142C><se_low>Yangus: I dunno wot to say... We done all we could,
but it just weren't enough, like...

<voice_0x0100142D><se_def>Angelo: I'm so sorry, Empyrea.
We failed you.
We couldn't save your egg...

<voice_0x01001430><center>Do not blame yourselves.
<center>I should never have put you in this position.

<voice_0x01001431><center>I am truly sorry for having brought
<center>you here and for subjecting you
<center>to such a bitter experience.

<voice_0x01001432><center>I will take you back to the Eye
<center>so you may return to the World of Light.
<voice_0x01001433><center>Mother! Wait!
<voice_0x01001434><center>M-My...baby?

<voice_0x01001435><center>Yes, it's me, Mother!
<center>Do not feel sad.

<voice_0x01001436><center>I wanted to give something to
<center>the people who came to help me.
<center>To thank them.

<voice_0x01001437><center>Give them something?
<center>But you're...

<voice_0x01001438><center>I know, Mother.
<center>But I can still help them.

<voice_0x01001439><center>I am just a soul. I have no form.
<center>But if they lend me their bodies,
<center>I can make them fly.

<voice_0x0100143A><center>Let me travel with you!
<center>I can help you!

<voice_0x0100143B><center>It is true.
<center>If my child can be of help to you on
<center>your quest, I hope you will accept.
<voice_0x0100143C><center>Please grant my son his wish to accompany you.

<voice_0x0100143D><center>Why would you deny him the chance to repay
<center>you? Please, grant my son his wish...
<center>He can accompany you where I may not follow.

<voice_0x0100143E><center>Thank you, <hero>.
<center>I cannot express my gratitude enough.

<voice_0x0100143F><center>I will change into a form that
<center>you can carry around with you.
<center>Whenever you need me, just call.
<voice_0x01001440><se_low>King Trode: Well, that was a singularly unusual affair.

<voice_0x01001441><se_low>King Trode: To think there is a whole other world!
If I hadn't witnessed it with my own eyes,
I'm quite sure I would never have believed it.

<voice_0x01001442><se_low>King Trode: And if that strange eye wasn't there,
I'd be convinced it had all been a dream.
<voice_0x01001429><center>What was that noise?

<voice_0x0100142E><se_high>Red: I'm sorry, Empyrea.
We let ya down...big time.
<voice_0x0100142F><se_low>Morrie: I disGUST myself, letting a bellissimo bird down. Empyrea, scusi. I hope that you find it inside your heart to forgive us.
